<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Home - Mera Portfolio</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; margin:0; background:#f5f7fb; color:#111; }
    header { background:#1f2937; color:#fff; padding:20px 16px; }
    nav a { color:#cfd8f1; margin-right:14px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:600; }
    nav a:hover { color:#fff; }
    .container { max-width:1020px; margin:auto; padding:24px; }
    .hero { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center; gap:24px; background:#fff; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(31,41,55,.12); padding:24px; }
    .hero img { width:180px; height:180px; object-fit:cover; border-radius:50%; border:4px solid #3b82f6; }
    .hero h1 { margin-top:0; margin-bottom:6px; font-size:2rem; color:#1e293b; }
    .hero h2 { margin:0 0 12px; font-weight:500; color:#3b82f6; }
    .bio { margin-top:14px; font-size:1.05rem; }
    .bio strong { color:#0f172a; }
    .skill-chip { display:inline-block; background:#dbeafe; color:#1e3a8a; padding:5px 10px; margin:4px 4px 4px 0; border-radius:999px; font-weight:600; }
    section { margin-top:24px; }
    h3 { color:#1e40af; }
    footer { text-align:center; margin:32px 0 12px; color:#475569; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <a href="index.html2">Home</a>
      <a href="project.ht">Projects</a>
      <a href="contact.ht">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/180" alt="Profile Photo" />
      <div>
        <h1>Namaste, Main Chandni</h1>
        <h2>Web Developer & Designer</h2>
        <p class="bio">Mera naam Chandni hai. Main <strong>frontend</strong> aur <strong>full-stack</strong> development mein kaam karti hoon. Mujhe <span class="skill-chip">HTML</span><span class="skill-chip">CSS</span><span class="skill-chip">JavaScript</span> pasand hai, aur main <span class="skill-chip">responsive layout</span>, <span class="skill-chip">a11y</span> aur <span class="skill-chip">UI UX</span> par focus karti hoon.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h3>Highlights</h3>
      <p>Yahan par main apne <strong>important words</strong> ko highlight kar rahi hoon, jaise ki <strong>performance</strong>, <strong>teamwork</strong>, aur <strong>innovation</strong>.</p>
      <div>
        <span class="skill-chip">Problem Solving</span>
        <span class="skill-chip">Agile</span>
        <span class="skill-chip">Git</span>
        <span class="skill-chip">API Integration</span>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <footer> 2026 Chandni. Sab rights reserved.</footer>
</body>
</html>
